Description: KDE - language files for Tamil
License: GPL/LGPL
Maintainer: Benjamin Reed <kde-i18n-tamil@fink.racoonfink.com>

Depends: kdelibs3-unified (>= %v-11), xfonts-intl
BuildDepends: fink (>= 0.24-1), arts-dev, kdebase3-unified-dev (>= %v-11), kdelibs3-unified-dev (>= %v-11), libxml2, libxslt, xfonts-intl
